column5: Glad I'm not the only one going through this! I was raped as a child too and ever since the assaults happened.. I've been feeling like a sex-craved maniac.
Absolutely! The smell of cigarettes and alcohol triggers me.
I bet it did. Well done! :)
Was abused in my childhood but I used to be like this when I was in High school. Although.. as I'm getting older, the more feminine I'm getting.
